{"tid":2023833,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中四男子承認向警察宿舍擲汽油彈候判 早上東區法院兒童庭審理","createTime":"2020-05-19T08:58:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T11:12:39.000Z","uid":21470,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"8d380666741c7506d4bc976d93373fa49195efe7","tid":2023833,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:58:00.000Z","msg":"男子承認向警察宿舍擲汽油彈候判<br />\n19.05.2020 16:46<br />\n<br />\n一名15歲中四男學生，去年11月向柴灣已婚警察宿舍投擲汽油彈，導致一名警長的寓所外牆及窗戶熏黑，他上午在東區法院兒童庭承認一項縱火罪，獲准保釋至7月14日，以等候感化官、社會服務令及心理報告。裁判官指，被告犯案性質嚴重，若已成年一定會判監，提醒被告犯案時可能認為好小的事，後果可以好大。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，去年11月18日下午，有途人發現被告與一名女子自向柴灣已婚警察宿舍投擲汽油彈，途人制服被告報警，女子則逃去。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1288528&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1288528%26csid%3D261_341&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F1lsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=2f14afac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1288528&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"d4f148c3e1121b9129ee4ae813bd488a66568bba","tid":2023833,"uid":260694,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:59:26.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，咩途人咁撚多事？"},{"pid":"0587b872ac183909b7f21ad087ee448c247af43d","tid":2023833,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:01:13.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"44630e2e571617bbb8319e87be40d106ce12b4ae","tid":2023833,"uid":113155,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"d4f148c3e1121b9129ee4ae813bd488a66568bba","tid":2023833,"uid":260694,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:59:26.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，咩途人咁撚多事？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:03:07.000Z","msg":"途人應該係收工嘅狗或狗子女"},{"pid":"eeac2bd7a1c337c00df3bed6a392771cc5c70502","tid":2023833,"uid":196701,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:03:53.000Z","msg":"原來手足咁高學歷"},{"pid"